{"tid":420878,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人識計自摸十三么既機會率？","createTime":"2017-10-01T18:01:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T18:42:51.000Z","uid":140706,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"608cf36b00ad8bd4cc6d5ba6b0e3adc1168ad161","tid":420878,"uid":140706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:01:27.000Z","msg":"今日同班親戚打麻雀<br />\n食左鋪自摸十三么<br />\n自摸嗰隻仲要係絕章北嚟<br />\n有冇巴絲識計個機會率出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好好奇個機會率會唔會比中六合彩二奬高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：冇玩錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b877813214ff9f979198b24ba53f0b29e9c2d4ce","tid":420878,"uid":17402,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:02:24.000Z","msg":"50/50<br />\n<br />\n一係中, 一係唔中"},{"pid":"57bf3bf694d3ea6c4ba929b8a7ea068d198ef6f2","tid":420878,"uid":140706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:06:51.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲識計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想知"},{"pid":"a77128b4b3060a62857cd06d120661549d3c7f88","tid":420878,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:07:46.000Z","msg":"成日食㗎啦<br />\n睇你有冇心做姐<br />\n六合彩二獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb575575e64ecd5878a14c60a16e52caae0432c7","tid":420878,"uid":10325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:08:22.000Z","msg":"食2粒腰果，哈哈，你就知道"},{"pid":"c61365c2cb591716fd6ab7550f898642107bc360","tid":420878,"uid":1807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:12:46.000Z","msg":"唔可以指定一章牌計<br />\n<br />\n如果只係計摸中機率 摸中機率大過清一色對對"},{"pid":"16b9d601e1d63255a897e8741da3a9813e2e2686","tid":420878,"uid":17402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:14:44.000Z","msg":"做個monte carlo simulation 咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22cfbb4f784ccaffe8b6959e2951477a99d67a5d","tid":420878,"uid":51308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:18:51.000Z","msg":"計叫十三飛 定 計單章先"},{"pid":"489426ce6a76f72c070e73aa51a99750e9564fcf","tid":420878,"uid":123647,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:20:42.000Z","msg":"唔識計4個人打，當你一條友亂抽想抽副食得出既十三么<br />\n<br />\n全部牌都有4隻，夾埋有144隻<br />\n<br />\n每摸出一隻果144隻就少1隻 <br />\n<br />\n當你摸曬13款既機會率就係4/144 x 4/143 x 4/142 x 4/141 x ..... x4/132 (好似係)<br />\n<br />\n再乘摸到對眼 3 x 13 / 131 <br />\n<br />\n個3係因為全部么九章都摸咗一隻所以得番每款都係淨返3章，13係因為13款是但一款都得，131就出面144抽淨131隻因爲你抽左13隻<br />\n<br />\n利申:9up，小學畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等高手solve"},{"pid":"ca52e7c781fe6484b8388ee6397d1d1cf3c9fb38","tid":420878,"uid":98626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:22:34.000Z","msg":"咦 叫我？"},{"pid":"55fbcb505211a270f3df69ebe0dc4bb55df0dd22","tid":420878,"uid":140706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:23:19.000Z","msg":"係計單章<br />\n因為我拎住兩隻一萬<br />\n只可以食到北咋<br />\n咁岩隻北係最後一隻<br />\n唔該哂巴打 好想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9d0abe4fe13836be55112e029422ca2cf6d6225","tid":420878,"uid":140706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:25:17.000Z","msg":"講漏野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有打八隻花牌<br />\n但我一隻都冇摸過<br />\n跪地求巴打答案  唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee6afd7e2a029e97c5cc23a788501fe2660315b","tid":420878,"uid":123647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:30:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係計單章<br />\n因為我拎住兩隻一萬<br />\n只可以食到北咋<br />\n咁岩隻北係最後一隻<br />\n唔該哂巴打 好想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n首先你拎住兩隻一萬對佢黎講去到叫糊階段已經冇分別<br />\n<br />\n佢食得出既機會率(如果冇人碰冇人上，同埋冇人打北)咁就 四份一。 因爲佢都係9摸，而冇人因爲碰上摸少隻(槓補牌尾所以有摸牌)<br />\n<br />\n都好睇有冇人叫緊糊，叫緊幾絕章啦，以上假設三家唔食糊摸到尾，同埋一定扣北"},{"pid":"c5b15d290d60f124f560c7ff847606bb3c2638fb","tid":420878,"uid":38462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:42:51.000Z","msg":"好細"}]}